title._content: Land Development at North Key Largo with "Plugged" Canals State Permits Are Required to Open Canals to the Ocean and These Permits Are Hard to Get. Developers Dig the Canals Anyway, and Buyers Can Hope That the "Plugs" Will Later Be Removed.
